We use the information collected exclusively to:

- Respond to your questions, requests, and messages;
- Share information about retreats, workshops, events, and practices at A Casa da Alquimia;
- Send communications about wellness, meditation, and ancestral practices when you choose to receive them;
- Improve the browsing experience on our website;
- Comply with legal obligations when necessary.

Your data will never be sold, rented, or shared with third parties for commercial purposes.

The processing of personal data by A Casa da Alquimia is based on the following legal grounds under Brazil's General Data Protection Law (LGPD — Law No. 13,709/2018):

- **Consent:** when you fill out our forms or subscribe to our communications;
- **Legitimate interest:** for statistical analysis of website usage and continuous improvement of services;
- **Contract performance or pre-contractual procedures:** when processing registrations for retreats and activities.

We may share your data only in the following situations:

- **Service providers:** email platforms, analytics tools, and payment systems, solely to operate our services — all bound by confidentiality obligations;
- **Legal obligation:** when required by competent authorities or court order;
- **Rights protection:** when necessary to enforce our legal rights.

Your data is **not shared** with marketing companies, advertisers, or any third parties without a direct relationship to our services.

Our website may use cookies and similar technologies to:

- Ensure correct page functionality (essential cookies);
- Analyze browsing behavior in an aggregated and anonymous way (analytics cookies);
- Display content from external platforms such as YouTube, Spotify, and Instagram embedded in the site.

You can configure your browser to refuse cookies or be notified when cookies are being sent. Disabling essential cookies may prevent some site features from working correctly.

This site embeds or contains links to third-party services, including:

- **Instagram, Facebook, and YouTube** — social networks governed by their own terms and privacy policies;
- **WhatsApp (Meta)** — used as a support channel;
- **Spotify** — audio player embedded for music and meditation content.

We recommend reading the privacy policies of each of these platforms, as A Casa da Alquimia has no control over the data they collect.

Under the LGPD, you have the right to:

- **Confirm** the existence of processing of your personal data;
- **Access** the data we hold about you;
- **Correct** incomplete, inaccurate, or outdated data;
- **Request anonymization, blocking, or deletion** of unnecessary or improperly processed data;
- **Portability** of your data to another service provider;
- **Revoke consent** at any time, without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing;
- **Object** to processing based on other legal grounds in case of non-compliance.

To exercise any of these rights, contact us at casadaalquimia@gmail.com. We will respond within 15 business days.
